        </a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Info Section -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">â„¹ï¸ Was wird getestet?</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-green-600 mt-0.5">âœ“</span>
          <span>Schema.org Markup fÃ¼r strukturierte Daten</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-green-600 mt-0.5">âœ“</span>
          <span>Semantisches HTML5 (article, section, nav)</span>
        </div>
